2 main tag in configuration .xml file
Appenders
Loggers

Where to log ? -- Appender Tag_ Console

In Appenders tag, if you give Console tag, out put will print in Console

prefix to message can be modified om 

if you give file tag, out put will print in File (require file)


What to log ? -- Loggers
<Root Level = "error"> - it willprint only error file/message into out put 
<Root Level = "trace"> - it will print entire out put

How to log ? -- Appender Tag_ Console_ Pattern Layout